Review this SolidJS 1.x component and refactor it to be more idiomatic without changing behavior. Explain the most important reactivity mistakes you fixed.

```tsx
function UserCard(props: { user: { name: string; age: number } }) {
  const { user } = props;
  const [count, setCount] = createSignal(0);
  const doubled = count() * 2;

  createEffect(() => {
    console.log(doubled);
  });

  return <div>{user.name} {doubled}</div>;
}
```

